***Taken online bc covid*** Take SOC3105 with this prof if you can! If you show up and do the work it should be an easy A. Graded based on discussion board participation, 2 assignments and a final. Extremely fair grading criteria imo. A little reading heavy but none of them were super dense/hard to get through.
Solid choice as he cuts the BS and lets you know what's important and is passionate in what he teaches and wants you to genuinely do well.
